			<h4>*STAGE 1</h4>
			Each or any of the <i>Terms, Concept or Specific Objects</i>[words] presented in Stage 1 may invoke personal feelings, spark a particular philosophical interest, connect with you on spiritual level, all three or none at all. Based on your understanding of the words, it’s up to you to reflect on your life’s experience and select the category, or categories, you feel best fit it.<br /><a style="font-weight:700;" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#reminder">UI Example</a>
			<br /><br />
			<img src="img/s1Img.jpg" style="float:left; margin:0 20px 15px 0;"/>
			<div>
				<strong>The four categories</strong><br />
				<ul class="about">
					<li>Man's View of Himself (Himself/Herself)</li>
					<li>Man's Connections with Other than Himself</li>
					<li>Man's View of the World</li>
					<li>Man's Physical Activities</li>
				</ul>
				<strong>The word "Man" simply means the <i>universal man</i> of which you are an example. <br />As such, you may:</strong><br />
            	<ul class="about">
					<li>Personalize any or all words to yourself</li>
					<li>Think of others exclusively</li>
					<li>Think of yourself and others together</li>
            	</ul>
				<strong>Trapezoid selection space</strong><br />
			<ul class="about">
				<li><a style="font-weight:700;" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#definition">Spiritual</a> -- incorruptible, intangible, genuine, and essential</li>
				<li><a style="font-weight:700;" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#definition">Material</a> -- composed of parts, occupies physical space, can be degraded</li>
				<li>Spiritual & Material converging -- the spiritual elevates, or adds depth to the material object while the material object strengthens the spiritual essence by being its physical embodiment. Together they're more than their parts.</li><br /><strong>Spiritual & material converging examples</strong>:<br />Hypothetical 1: Someone you know was stranded out at sea and all they had to drink was their own Urin. It saves their life. Niether of you may ever think about Urin the same way again.<br /> 
				Hypothetical 2: An out-of-control truck kills 5 people on the sidewalk your walking. To you, trucks aren't just for transporting cargo anymore.
				
			</ul>
