        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          
          <h3>Spiritual</h3>
           <ul>
          	<li><strong>incurruptable</strong>: cannot be reduced any further from what it is, what it means and how it opporates</li>
          	<li><strong>intangible</strong>: can't be held or touched. Has no physical presence</li>
          	<li><strong>genuin</strong>: something corroborates with what the mind knows it should be and what the thing actually is</li> 
          	<li><strong>essential</strong>: if you remove any part of the it, it ceases to exist</li>
           </ul>
          <h3>Material</h3>
          <ul>
          	<li><strong>composed of parts</strong>: remove one piece and it still exists albeit potentially in a limited way</li>
          	<li><strong>occupies physical space</strong>: has form and exists in space and time</li>
          	<li><strong>degradable</strong>: can be ruined or destroyed by a person or by time</li>
           </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
